.jumbotron
  %h1 Bible Challenges
  %p.lead BibleChallenges.com enables you to create a Bible reading challenge for a church, small group, or student organization.  Click below to get started.
  %center
    %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-success{href: new_creator_challenge_path} Create Your Challenge

  - unless @public_challenges.empty?
    %p Or take a look at some of the current challenges:

    %ul
      - @public_challenges.each do |challenge|
        %li= link_to challenge.name, "http://" + subdomain_url(challenge.subdomain)
